@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At <strong>Contract Monthly Claim System</strong>, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting
    the personal information of all users, including lecturers, coordinators, and managers who use this platform.
</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Personal details such as your name, email address, and contact information when you register.</li>
    <li>Claims data submitted by lecturers, including claim amounts, supporting documents, and remarks.</li>
    <li>Administrative actions taken by coordinators and managers for verification and approval purposes.</li>
    <li>System usage logs for security and auditing.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>To process, verify, and approve monthly claims.</li>
    <li>To generate invoices and maintain financial records.</li>
    <li>To improve the efficiency and reliability of the claim process.</li>
    <li>To ensure compliance with institutional and financial regulations.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>
    All claim records, attachments, and user information are stored securely in our database.
    We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your data from
    unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
</p>

<h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
<p>
    We do not sell or rent user information. Data is shared only with authorized coordinators,
    managers, and system administrators strictly for claim processing and auditing purposes.
</p>

<h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
<p>
    Users may request access to their data, correct inaccuracies, or request deletion where appropriate,
    subject to institutional data retention policies.
</p>

<h2>6. Updates to This Policy</h2>
<p>
    This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to reflect changes in legal, operational,
    or security requirements. Updates will be communicated through this page.
</p>

<h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
<p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled,
    please contact the system administrator at <a href="mailto:support@contractclaims.local">support@contractclaims.local</a>.
</p>
